<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Market Trends | FarmSarthi</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/stylehomepage2.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/trends.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("component/navbar.ejs") %>

  <header class="trends-header">
    <h1>📊 Market Trends</h1>
    <p>Latest agricultural market analysis to help you plan, sell smart, and stay ahead of competition.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="trend-list">

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🌾 Rise in Organic Wheat Demand</h2>
      <p>Urban health-conscious consumers are pushing demand for pesticide-free wheat. Premium prices up to 30% higher.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Growers can earn more by switching to certified organic methods.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>📉 Tomato Prices Dip in Monsoon</h2>
      <p>Excess harvest and poor storage during rains causes market saturation, leading to falling prices.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Use controlled harvesting + covered storage to time better market entry.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🍚 Basmati Export Market Expanding</h2>
      <p>Demand for premium Basmati is rising in Gulf and European countries. India’s export value rose by 14%.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Join export-grade programs or cooperatives to get better international rates.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🥔 Potato Prices Fluctuate Heavily</h2>
      <p>Overproduction in winter leads to crashing prices, followed by sudden spikes in summer scarcity.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Consider cold-storage access or staggered selling to optimize returns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🥬 Rise in Urban Microgreens Demand</h2>
      <p>Hotels & cafes are sourcing microgreens like arugula, basil, etc. from local growers for freshness.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Great opportunity for youth or rooftop growers near cities using hydroponics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>☀️ Heatwaves Impact Yield</h2>
      <p>Early heatwaves in northern states in March–April are reducing yields for wheat and mustard.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Shift to heat-tolerant seed varieties and adjust sowing cycles accordingly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🍇 Direct-to-Consumer Fruit Sales Rising</h2>
      <p>Consumers prefer fresh fruit deliveries directly from farms post-COVID, improving farmer margins.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Setup D2C delivery via WhatsApp/local ads or partner with platforms like FarmSarthi.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🧅 Onion Price Surges Continue</h2>
      <p>Frequent price hikes due to weather or storage problems keep onions volatile but profitable.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Bulk selling with buffer stock can turn volatile crops into high-profit ones.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>🌽 Demand for Animal Feed Grains Rising</h2>
      <p>Maize, bajra, and soybean used in poultry & dairy feed are in constant demand from agribusinesses.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Contract farming with animal-feed buyers gives assured returns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="trend-card">
      <h2>📦 Cold Storage Investments Increasing</h2>
      <p>Private cold chains expanding in tier-2 cities due to growing vegetable logistics demand.</p>
      <p class="insight">💡 Join storage co-ops or lease cold space to preserve perishables longer.</p>
    </div>

  </section>
  <%- include('component/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
